{"tid":509513,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung DRAM價格加幅太大！被中國控壟斷，仲俾人照埋肺","createTime":"2017-12-25T11:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T13:38:25.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b882f03fe036bc19f19c40db9a1bcddeadb7a20d","tid":509513,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/07115946/shutterstock_416365276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2F07115946%2Fshutterstock_416365276.jpg&h=c55645ce&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n記憶體價格連續 6 季上漲，2018 年第一季價格續揚，據傳中國不滿，質疑記憶體大廠涉嫌聯合壟斷價格，支那改革委員會已經約談三星電子，目前還不確定是否會展開反壟斷調查。<br />\n<br />\nHankyoreh 24 日引述中媒《21世紀經濟報導》稱，中國監管機構收到多家手機廠商投訴，開始關注記憶體價格飆漲問題，據悉支那改革委員會已經約談三星。<br />\n<br />\nDRAMexchange 數據顯示，11 月為止，DDR4 價格升至 3.59 美元；和 2016 年 6 月的 1.31 美元相較，上漲超過 2 倍。Hankyoreh 否認韓廠操控價格，表示價格飛漲是因全球供不應求，中方大動作是想施壓韓廠降價。<br />\n<br />\n韓國經濟日報 25 日社論稱，全球需求大增，DRAM 價格自然水漲船高。南韓佈署薩德飛彈防禦系統之後，中方一直找理由報復韓廠。中國自己蓄意拉抬稀土價格，卻用荒謬理由打壓南韓業者。<br />\n<br />\n25 日日韓股適逢聖誕節休市，對三星和 SK 海力士股價衝擊，要到 26 日才見分曉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2017/12/25/samaung-memory-price-monopoly-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2Fsamaung-memory-price-monopoly-china%2F&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f9ff0499\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2017/12/25/samaung-memory-price-monopoly-china/</a>"},{"pid":"5b5a9340eff2f6b8742c5082ee82ce78e8ccb3cd","tid":509513,"uid":658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"根本就係合謀加價<br />\n三星加價<br />\n其他廠可以唔加既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7e7685aaf2e4423bd89d594089eb0d7040f4a1","tid":509513,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"充公哂所有韓國貨啦一於<br />\n官員分哂佢"}]}